  </details>

  <h3><center>Cameras config</center></h3>

  starts with `cameras: {}` and put everything between the `{}`

  ```config
  cameras:
  {
      # here
  }
  ```

  Plugins have all different settings

  <h4>Default Plugin: Camera</h4>

  <details>
    <summary><u>Camera</u></summary>

    put config inside `()`

    ```config
    camera:
    (
        # here
    )
    ```

