    ```config
    {
        size= {x= 0, y= 0};
        transform= {
            position= {x= 0.0; y= 0.0, z= 0.0;};
            scale= {x= 0.0; y= 0.0, z= 0.0;};
            rotation= {x = 0.0; y = 0.0; z = 0.0;};
        };
        focal= 0.0;
        maxThreads= 0;
        filter= ();
    }
    ```
    (replace each 0 with your values)

  </details>

